snippet.title: Hungry Baby: Party Treats | Gameplay Trailer | Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Taste a unique recipe presented by the original publisher of Astro Bears Party and the creators of Timberman VS. 
Play with up to 4 friends as delicious treats in Hungry Baby: Party Treats, a funny and innovative local multiplayer game.

Find it now on Nintendo eShop! ⏩ http://bit.ly/HungryBabyPTeShop
